TY  - JOUR
TI  - Asset Valuation in an Experimental Market
AU  - Forsythe, Robert
AU  - Palfrey, Thomas R.
AU  - Plott, Charles R.
AB  - [The time path of asset prices is studied within a stationary experimental environment. After several replications prices converge to a perfect foresight equilibrium. A sequential market having an "informational trap" and a futures market are also studied.]
C1  - Full publication date: May, 1982
