TY  - JOUR
TI  - Two Stage Least Absolute Deviations Estimators
AU  - Amemiya, Takeshi
AB  - [In this paper the method of least absolute deviations is applied to the estimation of the parameters of a structural equation in the simultaneous equations model. A class of estimators called two stage least absolute deviations estimators is defined, their asymptotic properties are derived, and the problem of finding the optimal member of the class is considered.]
